                    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-300">Think of it like a factory that turns food into energy. Raw materials go in, they get processed, and fuel comes out to power the body.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-center">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-gray-700 rounded-lg flowchart-step">Receiving Dock <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold">▶</span> Mouth/Esophagus</div>
