                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-pink-500 text-center">The GU System</h3>
                    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-300">The GU system handles waste and reproduction. Think of it like a pool filter: the kidneys filter the urine, and the rest of the system drains and stores the waste.</p>
                     <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">Average Urine Production (Adult):</p>
                        <p class="text-6xl font-black text-pink-500 my-2">1-2 Liters</p>
