                    <p class="text-center mb-6 text-gray-300">The pain is not caused by the kidney stone itself, but by the pipe spasming around the stone.</p>
                    <div class="relative w-24 h-32 flex justify-center items-center overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="pipe w-6 h-full bg-pink-800 rounded-lg"></div>
