                <p>"Abdominal Trauma." StatPearls [Internet]. Treasure Island (FL): StatPearls Publishing; 2024 Jan-.</p>
                <p>"Gastrointestinal Bleeding." The Merck Manual, Professional Version.</p>
            </div>
        </footer>

